GeneralTexts.HomeIndexText:
This web site was created using Net_MVC_NLayer_Generator. The template allows you to create a Visual Studio 2013 solution based on 2 possibilities:

  • an ASP NET MVC web site
  • a .NET Multi-Tier application with an ASP NET MVC front-end website and WCF back-end application
The resulting solution can be desployed to Azure Web Sites or Azure Cloud Services depending on the selected choice and and has built-in features like:
  • Authentication and Authorization based on users and roles
  • WCF services are prepared to use NetTcp or Http bindings and UserContext is passed throughout messages.
  • ASP NET MVC website for mobile, desktop and tablet browsers
  • Logging exceptions at front-end and back-end tiers
  • User management
  • Globalization support
